review_content: Sealed pack, came with fan and little thermal paste on fan surface. Working fine.This is a fine CPU for office and home pc. An occasional gaming at low resolution may be supported. Audio-video-photo editing and conversions will also work fine if not required to be done in realtime.
Just awesome!!!!!Arrived before expected delivery date.4 GHz budget processor.
It's a 12th gen. LGA socket 1200 Great product by IntelAlso ideal for gaming users.
Arrived before expected timeline and in flawless condition. As for the product- its a Pentium Gold, nothing to write home about.
Given the cost of all processors hitting roof high, this processor was sufficient for building a computer for kids to attend online classes. Works very well
Good, receive sealed pack with good package
Best low budget CPU, We can play most mid level games without any problem. The only issue is the cover of CPU seal was open.
